34:20.658 --> 34:22.558
It's so warm, baby.

34:25.530 --> 34:28.988
Okay, that's it. Cleansing breath. Can I?

34:29.734 --> 34:31.099
- Yeah.
- Okay.

34:32.703 --> 34:34.102
There we go.

34:34.605 --> 34:38.166
Okay, girl, you concentrate now.
This is for the gold.

34:38.776 --> 34:39.970
Oh, God!

34:43.614 --> 34:46.481
You're a jackass.
You are a genuine jackass.

34:46.584 --> 34:47.710
Seriously,
there's no way she heard that.

