Well, are her swims always that short?

35:12.743 --> 35:16.907
No, she usually takes her time with it.
That's what I'm telling you.

35:21.252 --> 35:24.312
Oh, God. And now she's gone.

35:27.091 --> 35:28.251
- No!
- No!

35:28.359 --> 35:29.621
It's nothing. It's not her.

35:29.727 --> 35:31.194
Well, listen, it could be her.

35:31.295 --> 35:33.354
- It's not, so...
