35:38.736 --> 35:40.670
It's her at the door. It's her at the door.

35:40.771 --> 35:42.830
- No! No, no, no.
- Just look, look.

35:42.940 --> 35:47.604
- Shit! Don't, don't...
- Okay, okay, okay. Stop it. Okay.

35:47.712 --> 35:49.907
- Wait, wait, I got it.
- Oh, my God, we are so busted.

35:50.014 --> 35:52.414
- No, no, no! Wait! Don't answer it!
- I have to.

35:52.517 --> 35:55.577
She knows I'm here.
I got the thing on my foot.

36:00.725 --> 36:01.714
Hi.

36:02.360 --> 36:03.622
What took you so long?

36:03.728 --> 36:06.663
What... We were...
