36:08.332 --> 36:10.266
- Video games!
- Yeah. Video games.

36:10.368 --> 36:13.064
This is my friend, Ronnie. Ronald.

36:13.371 --> 36:15.464
- Say hi, Ronald.
- Hi, Ronald.

36:15.740 --> 36:17.332
You're so stupid.

36:17.708 --> 36:20.905
So, what brings you here?
To my house?

36:21.445 --> 36:24.437
- I got locked out.
- Oh, that sucks.

36:24.549 --> 36:26.039
It's a tragedy.

36:28.753 --> 36:30.778
So, you gotta call someone?

36:32.323 --> 36:35.383
No, I'd rather stay stranded,
if you don't mind.

36:36.194 --> 36:38.560
Video games, huh? I like to play.

36:43.367 --> 36:44.391
Is this your room?

36:44.502 --> 36:47.403
Just so you know,
it's a little messy, okay?

36:47.572 --> 36:49.972
- A little?
- Yeah.

36:51.309 --> 36:54.039
Anything interesting out here?

36:55.112 --> 36:56.306
The...

