43:03.547 --> 43:05.708
Oh, he's going for it.

43:07.351 --> 43:08.409
Okay.

43:09.153 --> 43:10.950
Here he goes. Here he goes.

43:11.255 --> 43:12.449
Denied.

43:15.492 --> 43:17.687
Look at the look on his face.

43:21.665 --> 43:23.963
