Here, take this.

43:37.314 --> 43:38.542
- No.
- No?

43:41.352 --> 43:44.150
No. Stop, stop.

43:44.655 --> 43:46.020
- No.
- Yeah.

43:46.123 --> 43:48.023
- You're kidding me.
- I think we got a match.

43:48.125 --> 43:49.422
Oh, God.

43:51.996 --> 43:53.463
It does match.

43:53.831 --> 43:55.458
Only in Disturbia.

43:56.333 --> 43:59.791
Where else are you gonna get
this kind of entertainment?

43:59.903 --> 44:03.168
- Thank God you moved here, right?
- Yeah.

44:11.849 --> 44:13.316
Wait a minute.

44:13.751 --> 44:16.811
Wait, did you see that?
Wait, zoom in a little.

44:28.666 --> 44:29.997
Oh, my God.

44:45.482 --> 44:47.541
Did you see that? The price tag.

44:47.651 --> 44:50.017
She won't be returning that dress.

44:56.960 --> 45:00.054
Oh, there you go.
Now you should bust your move.

45:04.635 --> 45:06.296
Who's the redhead?

45:06.937 --> 45:09.337
